name: INAUGURAL FLIGHT! KLM 787-9 Dreamliner [PH-BHA] Landing and Takeoff at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
On October 30th, KLM Royal Dutch Airlines began service to Calgary with their new 787-9 Dreamliner. For the winter 2016 season, the regular Calgary to Amsterdam flight will be operated by a 789 5 times a week and 772 1 time a week. Here we have the very first KLM 789 at Calgary International Airport landing and taking off, with ATC included! Enjoy.

Thanks for watching!
